[normal]Of the largest, “House Fittings and Appliances”, “Home maintenance and Improvements” was by far the largest with 30578 cases.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]From a sample of cases, we deduce that the majority of consumers already apply an “outcome based” standard to services provided.
